org_name: Mary McLeod Bethune Day Academy PCS

data: Extracurricular activities including sports, drama, tutoring and clubs
Focuses on positive character development and community service
Free transportation for students; bus stops located in all quadrants of the city
Half-day Spanish language immersion program for students in grades PK to 2; all classrooms have a 10:1 student-to-teacher ratio
Year-long instruction in art, music, foreign languages (Spanish and Latin), health and physical education
